window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>One great series in a single offering!</b></p> <p>Brandon's mundane existence is turned upside down the night he's shot at outside his office building. As if that weren't enough, he soon discovers that mythical creatures like Elves, Vampires, and Werewolves are not just the stuff of legend. And with the help of three alluring paranormal ladies, Silvana, Lina, and Johanne, he's about to embark on a journey he never could have imagined.</p> <p>Now, they're training him to be a killer. Preparing him for a battle that could decimate billions of lives, not just on Earth, but across the universe. A powerful evil has been unleashed, something that was banished eons ago, and it's slowly gaining strength. Brandon must face its minions head-on to prevent it from causing irreparable damage.</p> <p>With action-packed battles, mayhem, and magic, this series is not for the faint of heart. But if you're brave enough to join Brandon on his quest, you'll be treated to a world of monster girls, fluffy tails, and just plain lots of fun.</p> <p><b>Don't miss out on this thrilling adventure! Sit back, enjoy, and grab the popcorn. Download now and immerse yourself in the wild and wondrous world of Brandon and his paranormal entourage.</b></p>"; 
